  "text": "In this sense, corner voltage assignments on a map M are equivalent with voltage assignments on darts of the underlying graph of the medial map M m , representing just a different language for describing the lifting phenomena related to maps and their automorphisms. This is part of the folklore in topological graph theory; for details the reader is invited to consult [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
